    "title": "Speed Post India Advisory Limited is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Senior)",
    "description": "Speed Post India Advisory Limited invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Warehouse Manager at our Srinagar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Speed Post India Advisory Limited:\nSpeed Post India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Srinagar, Jammu & Kashmir, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Speed Post India Advisory Limited!",
